                </ul>
                <p><span class="bold">Acceptance of Changes:</span> By continuing to use the RGDC Dental Management System after the effective date of the updated Privacy Policy, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by the revised terms. Your continued use constitutes acceptance of the changes.</p>
                <p><span class="bold">Right to Object:</span> If you disagree with significant changes to this Privacy Policy, you have the right to:</p>
